# 2.11 Splitting and Joining Strings

## split()

```python
text.split()
text.split(",")
text.split("/")
```

## join()

```python
",".join(["a", "b", "c"])
"".join(["New", "York"])
"/".join(["home", "user", "docs"])
```

## Replace Separators

```python
title = "Python-Lab-Warmup"
tokens = title.split("-")
title = ":".join(tokens)
```

## Parse Key-Value Pairs

```python
pair = "State = DC"
tokens = pair.split(" = ")
```

